parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Cylinder #5 Glowplug Failure and Engine Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cylinder #5 glowplug can cause engine failure, leading to costly repairs and potential safety risks.

often accompanied by a loud noise or rumbling sound
making it difficult to maintain control of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank interior lining can cause debris to enter the fuel system, leading to engine stalling, poor engine performance, and potentially causing engine damage.
Contamination in the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the low power warning message displays on the message board
the vehicle is difficult or impossible to restart
the fuel system needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Tank Internal Rusting and Clogging
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Internal rusting of the fuel tank can cause fuel system clogs, leading to engine stalling, poor performance, and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel System Clogging due to Rusty Fuel Tank
